Important Parameters 

Config File:
    epoch_max # Max training epoch. 
    sam_checkpoint # Path of the pretrained SAM
    root_path_1 # Path of the train/test/val images 
    root_path_2 # Path of the train/test/val masks

adjust the image savining path:
   1. cv2.imwrite(args.save_dir + '/' + split + '/' + name_.split('/')[-1].replace('tif', '.png'), save_output)
   
args:   
    parser.add_argument('--config', default="configs/Example.yaml") 
    parser.add_argument('--name', default='Testcode', help="Name of the experiment. Set for saving")
    parser.add_argument("--orisize", type=int, default=1000, help="Save prediction in the original size of images")
    parser.add_argument("--patience_max", type=int, default=50, help="Train until the validation loss hasn't decreased for patience_max consecutive epochs")
    parser.add_argument("--test_epoch_start", type=int, default=50, help="Do not do testing per epoch until the test_epoch_start'th epoch")

